### Feature 2: Inline Calendly Popup Widget

Replace the `window.open()` call with Calendly's official popup embed widget so the calendar opens inside an overlay, not a new tab.

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/Projects/DHUMI%20Projects/US%20insurance%20chatbot/demo/index.html)

**Changes:**
- Add `<link href="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.css" rel="stylesheet">` to `<head>`
- Add `<script src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js"></script>` to `<head>`
