### Feature 4: Dynamic Tobacco-Adjusted Pricing Range

Currently the tobacco scenario shows a *note* but doesn't adjust the actual dollar range. We will compute real adjusted ranges.

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/Projects/DHUMI%20Projects/US%20insurance%20chatbot/demo/index.html)

**Changes in [showPricing()](file:///c:/Projects/DHUMI%20Projects/US%20insurance%20chatbot/demo/index.html#571-627):**
- Parse the base `range` string (e.g., `"$30-$45/month"`) into min/max numbers
- If `isTobacco`, multiply both by 1.5 and rebuild the string
- Display the adjusted range directly in the price card instead of just a warning note

